rComments: Prof. Suzuki is extremely helpful and approachable given the challenging subject material, and answers questions on the class's online forum very fast. Overall, a quality professor for econometrics/stats.

Suzuki is an extremely organized and helpful Prof. His lectures and slides were informative, and going to his office hour was beneficial. The concepts in the course itself are very difficult, and the final exam was difficult as well. This course is not for those who want to mess around.
